INSERT INTO `wp_options` VALUES(87, 0, 'widget_text', 'a:4:{i:2;a:0:{}i:3;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:685:"<img src="http://apiqe.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/globe.jpg"/>\n\nApiqe is committed to reducing the \neffect of plastic and glass bottles on \nour planet — and in helping consumers \nreduce their CO2 footprint. And it shows\n in our system:\n\n•  By replacing 250 bottles of water \n    each day, Apiqe can eliminate the \n    consumption of 1,368,750 gallons of \n    oil per year used to produced bottled \n    water\n\n•  Apiqe bottles can be reused several \n    times - they can withstand many \n    washing cycles using the same \n    washer used for plates, silver and \n    glasses\n\n•  Apiqe water has the lighter footprint in \n    the industry – less storage room is \n    needed ";s:6:"filter";b:1;}i:4;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:351:"<img src="http://apiqe.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/globe.jpg"/>\n\n• Most compact system\n• Most quiet system\n• Highest water rate\n• Lowest energy usage\n• Most customizable carbonation\n• Best filtration\n• Most safety features\n• Easiest to operate and maintain\n• Least costly\n• Lightest carbon footprint\n• Only system made in USA\n";s:6:"filter";b:1;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes');
