INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(222, 1, '2011-05-25 14:16:35', '2011-05-25 14:16:35', '<h1>revolutionary technology</h1>\r\n<img src="http://apiqe.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/doted-lines-short.png"/>\r\n\r\nFew industry breakthroughs have ever made such a big splash. Apiqe redefines standards in water purification and filtration. In fact the actual experience of drinking water will never be the same!\r\n\r\nApiqe works simply. More simply than others. Others may filter and cleanse water directly at the supply. But they’re bulky, multi-part and expensive. Unlike Apiqe.\r\n\r\nAt its heart is the Apiqe unit, a revolutionary technical innovation that reduces the filtration and purification engine to one simple valve. More about several patents? Purifier.   \r\n\r\nApiqe’s breakthrough technology is contained in one sleek unit — not just for aesthetics — but to minimize the carbon footprint. Connected simply to the mains, Apiqe is noiseless, saves space, time and money. It looks cool. It tastes even better.\r\n\r\nApiqe leaves behind contaminants and microorganisms. Leaving you with crisp water containing only the salts and minerals nature intended it to have — for drinking or cooking. \r\n\r\nAlways according to your preference. \r\nRoom temperature. Chilled, Hot, and Custom Carbonated to your desire.\r\n\r\n<h6>See our systems!</h6>', 'My Water', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'my-water', '', '', '2011-06-15 19:49:53', '2011-06-15 19:49:53', '', 0, 'http://apiqe.com/?page_id=222', 0, 'page', '', 0);
